{"id":472,"date":"2020-06-10T16:52:02","date_gmt":"2020-06-10T16:52:02","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/?p=472"},"modified":"2020-06-10T16:58:11","modified_gmt":"2020-06-10T16:58:11","slug":"live-stream-update-10-06-2020","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/2020\/06\/10\/live-stream-update-10-06-2020\/","title":{"rendered":"Live Stream Update (10\/06\/2020)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong><em>Titans!<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/EErhE0LpAsNf7_4I4m5mX-64HcgdExb4tqZSoOWwEXGn2uHV7q--vtm87lyCZfR5LyLY_Wy_apCqUbJOPubMmqjVbL380CQaePUU_4UxleYbNkXhxQPrY2w-OJ1H5zYlNwwIVso2\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Dawn of Titans team will not be able to bring you our scheduled Livestream over the next few weeks. We will instead get all upcoming event and Titan information to you through our blog every Wednesday.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But fear not &#8211; Matt, Dom and Haig will return, and we want to assure you that Dawn of Titans and the whole development team will continue working hard, running all events, releasing updates, and generally keeping the game awesome!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please note that the information below is not final, and certain aspects may be subject to change.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>CONTENTS<\/strong>:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Upcoming Schedule<\/li><li>Prestige Update<\/li><li>Alliance War &#8211; Divine Youkai<em> &#8211; <\/em>Event Details<ol><li>Titan Overview<\/li><li>Relic Overview<\/li><li>Milestone Rewards<\/li><li>Alliance Rewards<\/li><li>Chosen Titans and Boost Relic<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>DoT Content Creators<\/li><li>Social Channels<br><\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>UPCOMING SCHEDULE:<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Alliance War &#8211; <\/strong><strong><em>Divine Youkai &#8211; Oni<\/em><\/strong><ul><li>STARTS: 11th June, 14:00 UTC<\/li><li>ENDS: 15th June, 08:00 UTC<br><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>Kingdom Rush<\/strong><ul><li>STARTS: 15th June, 11:00 UTC<\/li><li>ENDS: 16th June, 11:00 UTC<br><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>Temple Event &#8211; <\/strong><strong><em>Altar of Everything<\/em><\/strong><ul><li>STARTS: 15th June, 14:00 UTC<\/li><li>ENDS: 18th June, 11:00 UTC<br><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>Alliance War &#8211; <\/strong><strong><em>Kami of the Divine Wind<\/em><\/strong><ul><li>STARTS: 18th June, 14:00 UTC<\/li><li>ENDS: 22nd June, 08:00 UTC<br><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>Titans Unleashed &#8211; <\/strong><strong><em>Rangers<\/em><\/strong><ul><li>STARTS: 22nd June, 11:00 UTC<\/li><li>ENDS: 23rd June, 11:00 UTC<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Theaters of War &#8211; <\/strong><strong><em>Earth<\/em><\/strong><ul><li>STARTS: 22nd June, 11:00 UTC<\/li><li>ENDS: 24th June, 11:00 UTC<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Alliance War &#8211; <\/strong><strong><em>Tusk &amp; Hide<\/em><\/strong><ul><li>STARTS: 25th June, 14:00 UTC<\/li><li>ENDS: 29th June, 08:00 UTC<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Spellcraft<\/strong><ul><li>STARTS: 29th June, 11:00 UTC<\/li><li>ENDS: 30th June, 11:00 UTC<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>PRESTIGE UPDATE:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh4.googleusercontent.com\/d4396FzWUvpJOPgVZ7PiWYyqO7F-AitTzYWSdGEi0vp2gSuPBmpPnlchppb0M0wta_sBPiWq-bR004BpFCw1rvxoYWf4VM6rNot68orZUwNWfQViG6n4uq1oCUgV5i6Z5r6-XSfJ\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Dawn of Titans team are excited to bring you one of our biggest updates yet &#8211; the Age of Prestige is almost here, so get ready to ENHANCE your Titans\u2019 power and abilities!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Over the next few weeks, we will begin rolling out the feature to an increasing number of players as we monitor the stability of the game. Rest assured, we will be working hard to ensure it launches for everyone as soon as it can.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To give you a little more information before the feature is unlocked for everyone, we\u2019d like to take you through the specifics of levelling up a Prestige Skill.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>LEVELLING UP YOUR TITAN\u2019S PRESTIGE<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In order to unlock the ability to Prestige your Titan, you <strong>must have reached level 60<\/strong> for the Titan you wish to Prestige.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once level 60 is reached, you will be able to start levelling up your Titan\u2019s Prestige skill from 1 to 10. To unlock level 1, you must <strong>Enhance<\/strong> your Titan using a single other 4* Titan of the <strong>same Element<\/strong> &#8211; the Prestige Skill <strong>does not automatically unlock<\/strong> at Level 1 once a Titan reaches level 60.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To further Enhance your chosen Titan\u2019s Prestige Skill, you will need to <strong>fill varying slots per level<\/strong>. The chart below shows how many slots are required for each level:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"391\" height=\"111\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-473\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture-1.png 391w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture-1-300x85.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 391px) 100vw, 391px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"420\" height=\"109\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture1-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-474\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture1-2.png 420w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture1-2-300x78.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>DUPLICATE BONUS<\/strong> is applied when levelling up a Titan\u2019s Prestige skill <strong>when 2 or more slots are required<\/strong>. For example, when levelling up a TOTEC from Prestige 7 to Prestige 8, you may fill the two slots with one duplicate TOTEC Titan. For levels that require <strong>only one slot to upgrade, the duplicate bonus will not apply<\/strong>, and any duplicate Titan used to level up will fill only one slot. The above tables show you the levels where this bonus applies, and the ideal level to use your duplicate Titans.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>All 4* Titans have a Prestige Skill<\/strong>. Some Titan\u2019s have <strong>Unique Prestige Skills<\/strong>, whilst others have a Prestige Skill <strong>based on their Titan Class &amp; Element<\/strong> combination. Unique Prestige Skill Titans require <strong>18 slots<\/strong> to max level their Prestige Skill &#8211; all other Titans require <strong>15 slots<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below is the<strong> list of current Titans that have Unique Prestige Skills<\/strong> (future Titans, either unreleased or re-skilled, may also receive Unique Prestige Skills):<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"313\" height=\"306\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture2-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-475\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture2-1.png 313w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture2-1-300x293.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 313px) 100vw, 313px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep an eye out for in-game messaging over the coming days which will reveal a number of these Titan\u2019s Unique Prestige Skills.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>ALLIANCE WAR &#8211; <\/strong><strong><em>Divine Youkai <\/em><\/strong><strong>&#8211; EVENT DETAILS:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a43ZApee63403NO7e2iREX_6kPfegxpavjcoyHgbunKwVSmbW-GNpJNGv4DuXMJn_OfSis931UDWHIKCiSGjMwchcCzxQGcYSIJOjX92jok3h3mnFxv8fzLOT2A_vE9Kag-QWpRh\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><em>Oni, Divine Youkai from the realm of demons, arrives in the Shattered Kingdoms to spread chaos and mischief among its inhabitants.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"533\" height=\"272\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture3-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-476\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture3-1.png 533w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture3-1-300x153.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Oni arrives with<strong> two signature Relics<\/strong>:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"477\" height=\"406\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-483\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture8.png 477w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture8-300x255.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 477px) 100vw, 477px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Milestone Rewards<\/strong> are as follows:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"315\" height=\"802\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/Capture5-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-478\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2